{"ID":270275, "Text":"<div class=\"page\"><div class=\"pageNum\"><a name=\"275\"><\/a><div class=\"prev\"><a href=\"stpjs274.html\">Prev<\/a><\/div><div class=\"next\"><a href=\"stpjs276.html\">Next<\/a><\/div>\n\t\t\t    STPJS 275<\/div>\n  <p class=\"cont\">is no better than other men; when he dies he is but a bag of dust.<span class=\"footRef\">1<\/span> I thank God for preserving me\n  from my enemies;<span class=\"footRef\">2<\/span> I have no enemies but for the truth&rsquo;s sake.<span class=\"footRef\">3<\/span> I have no desire but to do all men\n  good.<span class=\"footRef\">4<\/span> I feel to pray for all men.<span class=\"footRef\">5<\/span> We don&rsquo;t ask any people to throw away any good they have\n  got; we only ask them to come and get more. What if all the world should embrace this Gospel?\n  They would then see eye to eye,<span class=\"footRef\">6<\/span> and the blessings of God would be poured out upon the\n  people,<span class=\"footRef\">7<\/span> which is the desire of my whole soul.<span class=\"footRef\">8<\/span> Amen. (Jan. 22, 1843.) DHC 5:256-259.<\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">Politics<\/div>\n  <p class=\"cont\">To the Editor of The Wasp:&mdash;<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">Dear Sir: I have, of late, had repeated solicitations to have something to do in relation to the\n  political farce about dividing the county; but as my feelings revolt at the idea of having anything to\n  do with politics, I have declined in every instance in having anything to do on the subject. I think\n  it would be well for politicians to regulate their own affairs. I wish to be let alone, that I may attend\n  strictly to the spiritual welfare of the church.<span class=\"footRef\">9<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">Please insert the above and oblige.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"right\">JOSEPH SMITH.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"cont\">Nauvoo, Jan. 23, 1843.&mdash;The Wasp, Jan. 28, 1843, page 3.<\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">The Greatness and Mission of John the Baptist<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">The question arose from the saying of Jesus&mdash;&ldquo;Among those that are born of women there is\n  not a greater prophet than John the Baptist; but he that is least in the kingdom of God is greater than\n  he.&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">10<\/span> How is it that John was considered one of the greatest prophets? His miracles could not have\n  constituted his greatness.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">First. He was entrusted with a divine mission of preparing the way before the face of the Lord.<span class=\"footRef\">11<\/span>\n  Whoever had such a trust committed to him before or since? No man.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">Secondly. He was entrusted with the important mission, and it was required at his hands,<span class=\"footRef\">12<\/span> to\n  baptize the Son of Man. Whoever had the honor of doing that? Whoever had so great a privilege and\n  glory? Whoever led the Son of God into the waters of baptism, and had the privilege of beholding\n  the Holy Ghost descend in the form of a dove,<span class=\"footRef\">13<\/span> or rather in the<\/p>\n  <div class=\"footnotes\">\n    <div class=\"footnote\">1. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"105978\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 105978)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(105978)\">Gen. 3:19<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">2. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112538\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112538)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112538)\">3 Ne. 4:31<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">3. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109741\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109741)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109741)\">Gal. 4:16<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110630\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110630)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110630)\">2 Jn. 1:2<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">4. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109065\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109065)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109065)\">Acts 10:38<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109755\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109755)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109755)\">Gal. 6:10<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113131\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113131)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113131)\">D&amp;C 6:8<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"117211\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 117211)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(117211)\">A of F 1:13<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">5. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107847\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107847)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107847)\">Matt. 5:44<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111445\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111445)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111445)\">Enos 1:9<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">6. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107229\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107229)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107229)\">Isa. 52:8<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111637\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111637)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111637)\">Mosiah 16:1<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112192\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112192)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112192)\">Alma 36:26<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114734\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114734)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114734)\">D&amp;C 84:98<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">7. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115618\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115618)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115618)\">D&amp;C 110:9<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115797\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115797)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115797)\">D&amp;C 121:33<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">8. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107092\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107092)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107092)\">Isa. 26:8<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111446\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111446)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111446)\">Enos 1:9<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">9. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111778\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111778)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111778)\">Alma 4:20<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">10. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107940\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107940)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107940)\">Matt. 11:11<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108470\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108470)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108470)\">Luke 7:28<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">11. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108296\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108296)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108296)\">Mark 1:2<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">12. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115353\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115353)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115353)\">D&amp;C 105:10<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115926\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115926)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115926)\">D&amp;C 124:14<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">13. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107787\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107787)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107787)\">Matt. 3:13-16<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108631\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108631)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108631)\">John 1:32<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110968\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110968)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110968)\">1 Ne. 11:27<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111317\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111317)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111317)\">2 Ne. 31:8<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115016\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115016)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115016)\">D&amp;C 93:15<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>"}